name: Clarence E. FISHER, Petitioner v. COMMON PLEAS COURT, Respondent

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of September, 2011, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the “Petition for Writ of Mandamus and/or Extraordinary Relief Petition for Immediate for Hearing of Writ of Habeas Corpus” is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
